data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET READY FOR NEW OWNERS.  Hard to find property like this in town.  This 4 bed 3 bath Ranch style home sits on large lot with oversized 2-car garage (728sf), lots of extra parking, 40x47' heated shop with concrete, storage shed, alley access, 2 fenced in areas and a fully functioning greenhouse.  Lots of room for all your toys. No HOA or Metro Tax.  Wonderful home with new carpets in living area and Master bed. Primary bedroom and bath have been fully updated with large luxury shower.  Large eat-in kitchen with lots of countertop and cabinet space, SS refrig, gas oven/range, dishwasher.   Solar system to be paid for at closing,  many benefits with low or no electric bill even with the heated shop and fans in the greenhouse running.   Home is zoned multi-use, please verify.  All information is deemed to be correct, however Buyer to confirm.  Roof to be replaced and completed by closing.
